<i>noun</i>: 흉측 [흉측], 흉악 [흉악], 패악 [패ː악], 음흉 [음흉], 요사 [요사] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>흉측 [흉측]</dt><br>
<dd>brutality; wickedness</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 악하고 사나움.</dd><br>
<dd>A quality of being extremely evil and violent.</dd><br>
<dt>흉악 [흉악]</dt><br>
<dd>brutality; wickedness</dd><br>
<dd>성질이 악하고 사나움.</dd><br>
<dd>A quality of being evil and violent.</dd><br>
<dt>패악 [패ː악]</dt><br>
<dd>wickedness; viciousness</dd><br>
<dd>사람으로서 마땅히 해야 할 도리에 어긋나고 성질이 악함.</dd><br>
<dd>One's tendency to do things against the morality that a person should have; and one's personality being bad.</dd><br>
<dt>음흉 [음흉]</dt><br>
<dd>wickedness</dd><br>
<dd>겉과 다르게 속으로는 엉큼하고 흉악함.</dd><br>
<dd>One's state of mind being sly and cruel, different from what one appears to be.</dd><br>
<dt>요사 [요사]</dt><br>
<dd>capriciousness; wickedness</dd><br>
<dd>꾀가 많고 간사함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being capricious, clever or cunning.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>